<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>93</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A̱ki Chihowa ma!
 Himak akhlili ka,
 Chiso lilbʋsha sia hʋt
 Pit chi hoyo lishke.

[V2]
 Chisno pulla kak o̱,
 Sai okcha̱ya moma;
 Is sa halanli hatuk o̱,
 Ik sʋllo ki̱shʋshke.

[V3]
 Himak nitak oka,
 Nana achukma ka
 Is sʋm aiahni hatuk o̱,
 Ʋm achu̱kma moma.

[V4]
 Anukfilli li kʋt,
 Sa yukpa fehna hosh,
 Ʋba A̱ki pulla pit chi
 Aiokpanchi lishke.

[V5]
 Nan aiashʋche li
 Puta moma hoka
 Is sa̱ kashoffi pullashke,
 Chihowa A̱ki ma!

[V6]
 Himak okhlili ka
 Sʋlla he tuk ocha,
 Si ai illi hokmak heno,
 Is sʋshi pullashke.</lyrics>
<title>A̱ki Chihowa ma! ƲIT93</title>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
</song>